Welcome to my homepage on GitHub. Here you will find some of my open source projects.

#### Samuel
Samuel is a draughts game written in Python, PyGTK and C++.

#### [Hangman](http://johncheetham.github.io/hangman)
A version of the classic game in Python and PyGTK.

#### Breakout
Breakout game in Python and PyGame.
